      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPIN PAST (2) recorded her second win from three outings so far when she found the lead from one spot wider and kept going to score by close to 9 metres at Maryborough last week. A nice draw on the front line should see her push forward. Could deliver again. REGAL GALA (4) won two runs back then things went sour last time when he broke and finished a long way back. Has won a trial since so if he gets things right a big run is on the cards. ORLANDO VEYRON (3) produced a good effort on debut, finishing runner-up to REGAL GALA at Maryborough. Draws lower and has plenty of scope for improvement. MY LADY MAC (6) is another that can progress off a debut placing behind ZIPPIN PAST.",
